   <main>
     <header>
       <h1 class="bold">API Project: Parse Request Header</h1>
     </header>
    <section class="content">
      <h3>Description</h3>
      <p>A simple API microservice that extracts the IP address, preferred language, and system information from a request header
      <p>Make requests to '/api/whoami'</p>
      <p>The response will be a JSON object</p>
      <h5>Example Request</h5>
      <pre><code>GET https://parse-request-header.glitch.me/api/whoami</code></pre>
      <h5>Response</h5>
      <pre><code>{
  "ipaddress": "71.241.207.208",
  "language": "en-US",
  "OS": "Macintosh; Intel Mac OS X 10_13_6",
  "browser": "Chrome/70.0.3538.102 Safari/537.36"
}

      </code></pre>
    </section>
    <section class="form">
      <h3></h3>
      <form>
        <input type="text" name="date" id="input" placeholder="You can enter a date here to test it out" />
        <input type="submit" name="submit" id="submit" value="Go!" />
      </form>
    </section>
